1ยบ Install Ubuntu Release 12.04 (precise) 64 bit
2ยบ Install the script with the important apps
	-sudo sh installFirst.sh 
3ยบ Conky configuration
	-mv conkyrc /home/username/.conkyrc
	-go to System tools-->Preferences-->Startup applications
	-insert conky
4ยบ CompizConfig Settings Manager
	-check the following app in the Windows Management part:
		-Move Window
		-Put
		-Shift Switcher
		-Static Application Switcher
		-Grid
		-Resize Window
		-Scale 
		-Snapping Windows	
		-Windows Rules
	-Scale configuration
		-Go to Behaviour tab
		-Go to Multi Output Mode and select "On current output device"
		
